## Status legend

- `ok`: the configuration enables the readiness control or looks consistent for local review.
- `warning`: the configuration is accepted for labs but should be hardened.
- `manual`: the control needs human review or a runtime stack.
- `not enabled`: the readiness feature is disabled in the current config.
- `out of scope`: the control belongs to a later platform workflow.
